  m_text: "\nAs a <b>Explorer</b>, you will experience this land as it is. \r\nIt
    won't be easy, you will have to find a way to keep on going by your own.\r\nBut
    step by step, you will learn, and you will overcome it.\r\n\r\nIf you aren't
    into that idea however, you can be an <b>Observer</b> instead! \r\nThink of it
    as starting your journey with a few essentials already in hand. The world remains
    the same. You still need to move forward and see the it for yourself, but the
    journey is more comfortable now.\r\n\r\nWhichever way you choose, eventually,
    you will meet <b>her</b>. \r\n\r\nShe knows this place, and she will help you
    through it. \r\nAnd if you are willig...\r\nshe may even show you another way
    to explore this world."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
