      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "\r\n<b>MISC</b>\r\n\r\nNext is, uhh, about the lore, huh. That's right,
    lore, every game has to have one.\r\n\r\n ...\r\n\r\n .....\r\n\r\n ........\r\n\r\n
    This is no good, I never come up with any.\r\n\r\n [Come, help me a bit!]\r\n\r\n
    ...\r\n\r\n \"Evil forces have stolen the Mint Fumo away. We need to take them
    back!\"\r\n\r\n [Are you sure this is gonna do it?]\r\n\r\n [Alright then...]\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
