--- !u!114 &935231740
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 935231738}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '...


    Hi! It''s me!

    Borrowing her notebook a bit because I want
    to leave a few words here.


    First of all, thanks for playing!


    Since
    you are reading this, you must have made a good progress on this game already.
    You see, this page only exists after you have unlocked all 3 branches in her
    research.


    It''s been a journey. Hope you enjoyed the ride. And maybe this
    lab.


    Silly game, isn''t it?

    Yeah, I''m glad you think so, too.


    Hehe...


    Now,
    I told her to not read what I''ve been writing here.


    In the making of this,
    I digged through her files and read it over and over again.


    Mint really
    is cute, isn''t she?

    Even if you knew her before, even if you didn''t. Surely.

'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
