  m_text: "\r\n \"Your journey is going to be a long and difficult one. But worry
    not, because you are not alone!\"\r\n\r\n \"With your companions, with her inventions,
    any obstacle can be overcome!\"\r\n\r\n ...\r\n\r\n [This is really not getting
    anywhere...]\r\n\r\n [It's ok, let me just drive them off.]\r\n\r\n Uhmm, that
    was a bad one, isn't it... Sorry about that, we tried.\r\n Anyway, just play
    and see for yourself!\r\n\r\n Enjoy!\r\n\r\n ...\r\n\r\n [Phew, it's exhausting...]\r\n\r\n
    [Are the cookies ready yet?]\r\n\r\n"
