      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '

    Say, I loved the process of making this.

    I love brainstorming
    ideas. I love the gameplay. I learnt a lot. And I gave my best.


    But, my
    biggest goal with this, was to depict her as best as I could.


    I''m happy
    about what I accomplished here, and that I was finally able to introduce her
    to you.


    She won''t see this, so don''t tell her, okay?'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5e61686ba236ff04b8632d6a26736acd, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2509212030381675100, guid: 5e61686ba236ff04b8632d6a26736acd, type: 2}
