  m_text: '

    <b>INTRODUCTION:</b>


    Hi!


    This is Fumo Recu!

    A game
    about retrieving Fumo.


    Thanks for reading!


    ...


    [It''s too short?]


    [My
    bad, here, let me expand it a bit.]


    "Control your character, reach the
    location of the Mint Fumo to complete the stage, overcome different challenges,
    diverse your builds, and experiment with your own strategies".


    There we
    go.

    And well, yeah, that should pretty much sum it up!


    [Okay, how
    about now?]

'
