  m_text: '

    <b>DISCLAIMERS:</b>


    This is a passion project, dedicated to
    Arknights and the Mint of Arknights. I do not intend to profit from it, and it
    is not affiliated with, sponsored by, or endorsed by any third parties, companies,
    or organizations.


    Any characters, ideas, or elements inspired by existing
    works are respectfully acknowledged as their respective creators'' property.
    This project is purely for personal enjoyment and creative expression.


    All
    character sprites, some soundtracks, SFXs and VFXs are from Arknights, I do not
    own them by any means.


    If you have concerns or questions regarding the
    content, please feel free to contact me via my email: kimnguu2743@gmail.com.



'
